title: BullseyeüéØ Tie&Dye | all steps in the description. #shorts #tiedye #youtubeshorts
description:
Bullseye Tie&DyeüéØ
Detailed steps of this technique are  mentioned below üëá

Step 1:¬†Prewash the fabric with Prewashing Fixative powder for 20 minutes and squeeze off excess water from the fabric and keep it damp.

Step 2: Pinch the tshirt from the middle and pull the fabric to tie it. 

Step 3: Tie it with rubber bands to give atleast 5  sections and dye them with different colors of choice.

Step 4: Flip the tied fabric to the other side and dye it with same colors in sections.

Step 5: Zip it for 12-24 hours. The longer you keep, the better the color vibrancy.

Step 6: Pour all of Dyfix Mini bottle in 5 Liters of water and submerge your fabric in it for 15 minutes. Dyfix fixes color on your fabric and increases the color vibrancy.

Step 7: Wash off excess dye color with tap water and avoid direct sunlight while drying.

Did you like the results? Tell us in the comments below üëá 
Don‚Äôt forget to save it for later. We would love to see you all trying out this technique ‚ô•Ô∏è‚ú®

About this video: If you want to know how to quickly download and install Minecraft mods in 2026, this is the video for you. In this short video, we go over everything you need to know about Minecraft mods in 2026. 

First things first, you will need to download and install Forge for Minecraft. The good news is we have a complete guide on getting Forge in the description above. 

Once you have Forge, we can move on to downloading Minecraft mods. There are thousands of mods to choose from, and we have a link in the description above to CurseForge where you will find all of the most popular Minecraft mods out there. 

When downloading mods, just make sure they are for Forge and for the version of Minecraft you are downloading. For example, Minecraft 1.20.1 mods won‚Äôt work in Minecraft 1.20.4. The mods must be for the Minecraft version and Forge version you have installed. 

With your mods downloaded, we can install them. Open Minecraft with Forge, click the ‚Äòmods‚Äô button, and click ‚ÄòMods Folder‚Äô in the bottom left. 

Now, drag-and-drop the mods you downloaded into the mods folder. It‚Äôs that easy to install mods in Minecraft 2026. 

In order for your mods to work though, you will need to restart Minecraft making sure that you are playing Minecraft with the Forge installation. Your mods will only work if you play with the Forge installation. 

And when Minecraft opens, your mods will be installed. Congrats! You now know how to add mods to Minecraft in 2026. 

If you have any questions about how to get mods, let us know in the comments. We will try our best to help you out.

A dynamic PETRONAS green flow line anchors the design, sweeping low across the car to emphasize speed and precision while harmonising the transition from iconic Mercedes silver to the team‚Äôs deep black. 

The top of the sidepods feature the AMG-specific inspired rhombus signature, complimenting the iconic Mercedes three-pointed star pattern on the engine cover.

title: Why White Women Look Better On Camera
description:
For years, cameras and Hollywood lighting were basically designed with only white skin in mind - using something called Shirley Cards, which showed a white woman as the color reference. 
That meant darker skin often looked flat or lost in the shadows. Even facial recognition tech today struggles more with darker skin, especially darker-skinned women. 

Sources:

- L. Roth, "How Kodak's Shirley Cards Set Photography's Skin-Tone Standard," NPR, 2014
- John Akomfrah‚Äôs work on Shirley Cards and color bias, National Gallery of Art, 2023
- Joy Buolamwini and Timnit Gebru, "Gender and Skin-Type Bias in Commercial AI Systems," MIT News, 2018
- Google Real Tone initiative overview, Google Store, 2021 (Tulsee Doshi, Google's Head of Responsible AI)
- Toronto artist Farihah Aliyah Shah confronting Shirley Card bias, CBC Arts, 2022

#ShirleyCard #PhotographyHistory #ArtHistory #InclusiveTech #SkinTone

--- Un serpent id√©al pour d√©buter ? ---

Tr√®s appr√©ci√© par les amateurs de reptiles, le serpent des bl√©s ( Pantherophis guttatus ) est √©lev√© en captivit√© depuis de nombreuses ann√©es, le rendant ainsi assez docile, facile √† manipuler et √† entretenir. C'est exactement pourquoi cette race est l'un des meilleurs serpents animaux de compagnie disponibles pour d√©butants.
Les serpents des bl√©s sont disponibles dans notre animalerie de Lyon sous une multitude de motifs et couleurs.

---  Am√©nagement du terrarium ---

Le serpent des bl√©s a besoin :
‚Ä¢ D‚Äôun terrarium : Il est conseill√© de mettre le juv√©nile dans un petit terrarium de croissance (30 x30 x 30) pour √©viter le stress et afin de l‚Äôaider √† mieux √©voluer et s‚Äôalimenter correctement.
‚Ä¢ D‚Äôun substrat : Il est recommand√© d‚Äôutiliser des substrats neutres comme le Litaspen qui n‚Äôest pas poussi√©reux, tr√®s absorbant et sans danger en cas d‚Äôingestion.
‚Ä¢ D‚Äôun tapis chauffant avec un thermostat : √âtant donn√© que les serpents des bl√©s sont des animaux √† sang froid, ils ont besoin d‚Äôune source √† chaleur.
‚Ä¢ D‚Äôune gamelle d‚Äôeau : L‚Äôid√©al est de changer l‚Äôeau tous les jours.
‚Ä¢ D‚Äôune bo√Æte humide avec de la sphaigne (Mousse naturelle assez acide, qui garde l‚Äôhumidit√©.
‚Ä¢ D‚Äôune bo√Æte de ponte avec de la sphaigne pour les femelles reproductrices.
‚Ä¢ D‚Äôune cachette ou encore des branches.
‚Ä¢ D‚Äôun √©clairage du type Led (ce n‚Äôest pas indispensable): Pour cr√©er une luminosit√© si la pi√®ce n‚Äôest pas √©clair√©e naturellement.

Remarque : 

1. Pour les adultes, le terrarium et les accessoires doivent s‚Äôadapter √† la taille de l‚Äôanimal.
2. C‚Äôest possible de maintenir plusieurs serpents des bl√©s ensemble, mais il faut √©viter de mettre un grand et un petit sp√©cimen.

---  Alimentation ---

Les serpents de bl√©s sont relativement faciles √† nourrir et peuvent √™tre nourris avec des souris d√©congel√©s ou de petits rats pr√©d√©coup√©s. https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUznMD2lFth3arCFru0IQjg/join

If you are able to defeat the difficult Grinning Beast boss at the beginning of Look Outside, you gain access to a powerful secret ally. Going back to the room the Beast burst out from, you will find Leigh. A rugged, wide eyed NPC who is actually the Grinning Beast we just fought. Unlike the other abominations we find around the apartment complex, Leigh has unique control over her form and can morph at will and can do so in battle. She serves as a berserker type class as transforming in battle will have her confused for one turn where she can hit party members, but after the turn is over, you can control her Grinning Beast form. Her personality is just as erratic as her fighting style as she wants to rematch and fight Sam and other party members while in the apartment. However, having her allows the Rat Baby to grow faster as she will feed him her blood and encourage him to get stronger.
